- `premiumByItemType` → `basePremiumByItemType`: better reflects what the table now holds (pre-surcharge, pre-fee values)
- `runScenario`: still fits the broader scenario-runner intent
- New intermediate variables (`basePremium`, `withSurcharge`, `premium`) form a readable narrative

